User Interfaces: 

The user interface for the software shall be compatible to any browser such as internet explorer, mozilla
The user interface shall be implemented using tool or software package like Java Applet , Python and ….

Hardware interfaces: 
Since the application must run over the internet, all the hardware shall require to connect internet will be hardware interface  for the system. 
Modem, WAN-LAN-Ethernet Cross-cable and zo..


